original_title: สาระแน โอเซกไก
overview: Pranksters Willie and Hoi travel to Japan, the land of candidness, to seek new inspiration. The find the Yashimoto School of Candiness and become devoted students. Willie and Hoi try to accomplish their mission of playing pranks on five Thai superstars to prove themselves as worthy apprentices.
title: Saranae Osekai
